# UI Design Rules

## Design System

Framework:

* Ant Design

Design Style:

* Modern Healthcare
* Clean
* Data Intensive
* Accessibility First

---

## Color System

Primary:

#1677ff

Success:

#52c41a

Warning:

#faad14

Error:

#ff4d4f

Info:

#13c2c2

Background:

#f5f7fa

Card Background:

#ffffff

---

## Layout Rules

Use:

Header

Sidebar

Content

Footer

Responsive Design Required.

---

## Typography

Font:

Inter

Fallback:

Roboto

Font Sizes:

12

14

16

20

24

32

---

## Dashboard Principles

Users should understand:

* Queue Status
* Patient Status
* Waiting Time
* Department Load

within 5 seconds.

---

## Admin Dashboard

Widgets:

Total Patients

Waiting Patients

Completed Visits

Revenue

Department Utilization

Live Queue Status

Hospital Heatmap

AI Alerts

Recent Activities

Audit Logs

---

## Doctor Dashboard

Widgets:

Current Queue

Priority Queue

Patient Summary

Clinical Orders

Lab Results

Patient History

Quick Actions

---

## Receptionist Dashboard

Widgets:

Patient Registration

Manual Check-in

Insurance Verification

Ticket Printing

Payment Collection

Queue Assignment

---

## Laboratory Dashboard

Widgets:

Waiting Samples

In Progress

Completed

Result Upload

Queue Status

---

## Pharmacy Dashboard

Widgets:

Pending Prescriptions

Preparing

Ready For Pickup

Delivered

Patient Queue

---

## Patient App

Screens:

Login

Registration

Triage Form

Body Map

Queue Tracking

Payment

Navigation

Notifications

Medical Journey

Profile

---

## Kiosk UI

Must support:

Large Touch Targets

High Contrast

Simple Navigation

Elderly Friendly UX

Vietnamese Language

English Language

---

## Tables

Use Ant Design Table.

Features:

Pagination

Search

Sorting

Filtering

Column Visibility

Export CSV

---

## Cards

Use Cards for:

Patient Summary

Doctor Summary

Department Status

Queue Information

Statistics

---

## Charts

Preferred:

Line Chart

Bar Chart

Area Chart

Heatmap

Donut Chart

Avoid:

3D Charts

Decorative Charts

---

## Status Colors

Emergency

Red

Urgent

Orange

Routine

Green

Completed

Blue

Cancelled

Gray

---

## Notifications

Types:

Success

Warning

Error

Info

Use:

Toast

Notification Drawer

Realtime Badge Counter

---

## Accessibility

Support:

Keyboard Navigation

Screen Readers

High Contrast

Responsive Layout

Large Font Option

---

## Loading States

Every API request must have:

Skeleton

Spinner

Empty State

Error State

Never leave blank screens.

---

## Realtime UI

Update automatically:

Queue Position

Waiting Time

Payment Status

Lab Results

Navigation Route

Notifications

Use Socket.IO.

No manual refresh required.
